---

## Critical Files

- `src/schemas/manifest.ts` ← new
- `src/schemas/registry.ts` ← new
- `src/schemas/validate.ts` ← new
- `src/config/manifest.ts` ← rewrite `validateManifest` + `validateSkillEntry`
- `src/core/ownership.ts` ← rewrite `loadRegistry` guard
- `src/index.ts` ← rewrite agent ID loop in `parseCLI`
- `package.json` ← add `zod` dep + `@standard-schema/spec` devDep

---

## Verification

1. `npm install` — installs `zod` and `@standard-schema/spec`
2. `npm run typecheck` — ensures schemas infer correct types
3. `npm test` — all existing tests must pass, especially `test/manifest.test.ts` (10 tests checking specific error message substrings) and `test/ownership.test.ts`
